      <section class=3D"article-info">
        <div class=3D"article-content">
          <div class=3D"article-body"><p>Upon specific criteria, we can ini=
tiate an EDD KYC Recheck policy, in which case a client will be required to=
 provide POI, Selfie and in some cases undergo Phone verification. We can m=
onitor the client's progress in SumSub. If the client submits all required =
documents, our system will automatically approve the application. Before th=
e KYC Submission is successful, the client cannot operate the following act=
ions:</p><ul>
<li data-list-item-id=3D"e9494299c69f65519c7d351e27dc4b32f"><span data-team=
s=3D"true">Internal transfer requests</span></li>
<li data-list-item-id=3D"e79792e940d71a38213125853ec5b0964"><span data-team=
s=3D"true">Same-name account applications</span></li>
<li data-list-item-id=3D"efaadaf6adf8668432905f107dba8effa"><span data-team=
s=3D"true">Withdrawal requests</span></li>
</ul><p>There is a number of reasons why company can initiate a KYC recheck=
 process:</p><ul data-start=3D"166" data-end=3D"290">
<li data-start=3D"207" data-end=3D"244" data-list-item-id=3D"ebe6026e0c61f4=
06211ea3ab5c4fcdc9a">RC &amp; Compliance required</li>
<li data-list-item-id=3D"eee32b027c4e8e5faa9f9ceb0e9c06fbb">Entity Changing=
 (MAU and SVG)</li>
<li data-list-item-id=3D"eb62c55470f893cb1cc585d774be89452"><a href=3D"http=
s://mhknowledge.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/13191542616463-MH-Markets-KYC=
-Recheck-Policy#h_01K105EMKKA4T3ERA4NA1YFMKA">Expired documents (ID)</a></l=
i>
<li data-list-item-id=3D"e7f001c3d23fb43a6c577e73f1cc85f95"><a href=3D"http=
s://mhknowledge.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/13191542616463-MH-Markets-KYC=
-Recheck-Policy#h_01KF0WMG4M95CXPV6HSJ79MDVS">Suspicious Financial activity=
</a></li>
<li data-list-item-id=3D"e464c5a5810b1ddb749e4fb84a6447998"><a href=3D"http=
s://mhknowledge.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/13191542616463-MH-Markets-KYC=
-Recheck-Policy#h_01KF0WNFNKVE1RFN5RHST3KARK">USDT Withdrawal Selfie Step (=
Email Verification =E2=80=93 Manual Trigger)</a></li>
<li data-list-item-id=3D"e953802c590b17c6854aacfa631022dbb"><a href=3D"http=
s://mhknowledge.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/13191542616463-MH-Markets-KYC=
